quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Gom…óii malaama gom…óin…ìe …ìen
  23,2,∆Åen huloo…ìe ka nder Julde ma…ì…ìe ko…ìe yankinii…ìe
  23,3,E …ìen …óurnii…ìe gaayi rayrayti( bolle meere)
  23,4,E …ìen ittoo…ìe jakka on
  23,5,E …ìen reenu…ìe farjuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin
  23,6,"Si wanaa e dow sonnaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe maa…óum …ìe √±aame ma…ì…ìe …óen jeyi(horbe), haray kam…ìe …ìe wonaa feletee…ìe"
  23,7,"On mo …óa…ì…ìi …ìaawo …óum, haray ko …ìen woni jaggitoo…ìe …ìen"
  23,8,E …ìen aynu…ìe koolaaje ma…ì…ìe e aadiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin
  23,9,E …ìen …ìe ka√±un ko…ìe reenu…ìe e dow Jul…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen
  23,10,"∆Åee [sifor…ìe …óii sifaaji …óoo] ko kam…ìe woni ronoo…ìe …ìen"
  23,11,∆Åen ronoyay…ìe Firdawsi on kam…ìe ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe e nder makko
  23,12,Gom…óii Men tagii ne…ó…óanke on immorde e lasili loopal
  23,13,"Refti Men wa…ói mo to…ì…ìere [maniiyu] e nder √±ii…ìirde hu…ìindiinde"
  23,14,"Refti Men Tagi to…ì…ìere nden he…ó…óere, Men Tagi he…ó…óere nden huyre, Men Tagi huyre nden ∆¥i'e, Men holtini ∆¥i'e …óen teewu. Refti Men fu…ó…óanii mo Tagu woo, barkanii Alla Mo∆¥∆¥o Tagu…óo"
  23,15,Refti onon …ìaawo …óum ko on maayoo…ìe
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon √ëalnde Darngal on imminoyte"
  23,17,"Gom…óii Men Tagii dow moo…óon …óati jee…ói…ói, Men wonaali kadi welsindii…ìe gaayi tagu ngun"
  23,18,"Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam e emmbere [haaju tagu ngun], Men ndewni …óam ka leydi, pellet, Menen ko Men Hattan…ìe e dow na…ìugol …óam"
  23,19,"Men fu…ó…óani on sabu majjam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on nder ton dim…óe …óuu…óu…óe ko e majje √±aamoton"
  23,20,"E leggal ngal no yalta immorde to Tuuri Siinaa hingal fu…óina gu∆¥am [nebban wujetee…óam] e li'am [maafir…óam] wonannde √±aamoo…ìe"
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on e neemoraa…ói …óin tasakuyee, Me…óen yarna on go…ó…óun e ko woni kon ka deedi majji, no woodani on e majji nafaaji …óuu…óu…ói, ko immorde e majji kadi √±aamoton"
  23,22,Ko e hoore-majji e hoore laa…óe …óen ronndete…óon
  23,23,"Gom…óii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yim…ìe makko …ìen, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, rewee Alla. Rewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori Mo. Enee, on hulatah"
  23,24,"Hooree…ìe mbatu ngun wi'ani …ìen yeddu…ìe immorde e yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"Oo wonaali si ko o …ìanndinke yeru mo'on himo faalaa nde o …ìurnotoo e dow moo…óon. Sinndo Alla muuyino O jippinayno Malaa'ikaa…ìe, men naniraali …óum baabiraa…ìe amen aran…ìe …ìen"
  23,25,"Kanko o wonaali si wanaa ko o gorko mo jinna woni e mu'un, habbitee mo tun haa see…óa"
  23,26,"O maaki: \"Joom am, wallam e ko …ìe fennimi kon"
  23,27,"Men wahayini faade e makko yo o lesu laana kan e dennka Amen e Wahayu Amen, si Yamiroore Amen nden arii hu…ì…ìinirde nden pullitike [ndiyam] naadu e nder makka immorde e kala nooneeji …óin …ói…ói-…ói…ói. E koreeji ma, si wanaa …ìen konngol ngol aditii e mu'un, wata a haaldu e am fii …ìen too√±u…ìe, pellet, kam…ìe ko …ìe yooletee…ìe"
  23,28,"Si a fotondirii an e …ìen wonndu…ìe e maa…óa e dow laana kan, haray maaku: \"Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, On danndu…óo Men immorde e yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  23,29,"Maaku: \"Joomam, jippinam e jipporde barkinaande ko An woni Mo∆¥∆¥o Jippinoowo"
  23,30,"Pellet, no e nder …óum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo] Aayeeje, haysi men laatike ko men jarribotoo…ìe"
  23,31,Refti Men fu…ó…ói …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe yiirde wo…ì…ìe goo
  23,32,"Men Nulii e ma…ì…ìe Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e ma…ì…ìe, …óum woni Rewee Alla, rewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori Mo. E on hulatah [Mo]"
  23,33,"Batu e yim…ìe makko …ìen yeddu…ìe …ìe fenni hawroygol e Laakara on, Men neemini …ìe ka ngurdan aduna wi*i: \"Oo wonaali si wanaa …ìanndunke yeru moo…óon himo √±aama ko √±aamoton kon himo yara kadi ko yaroton kon"
  23,34,"Mi woondii si on …óoftike …ìanndinke yeru mo'on, pellet, haray onon ontuma ko on hayru…ìe(pertube)"
  23,35,"Enee, o fodu on wonndema onon si on maayii on laatike mbullaari e ∆¥i'e, wonndema onon ko on yaltinoytee…ìe"
  23,36,Wo…ó…óii woori kon ko foda…óon
  23,37,"[∆Åe wi'i:] \"∆äum wonaali si wanaa nguurdam amen aduna, me…óen maaya men wuura kadi, menen men wonaali immintinoytee…ìe"
  23,38,"Kanko o wonaali si wanaa ko o gorko fefindii…óo fenaande fawi e Alla, menen non, men wonaali gom…óinay…ìe mo"
  23,39,"O maaki: \"Joom am, wallam e ko …ìe fenni lam kon"
  23,40,"O Daali: \"See…óanii tun, Mi woondii …ìe wontay nimsu…ìe"
  23,41,"Haacaango ngon nanngi …ìe e Goonga, Men wa…ói …ìe duu√±o, halkaare wonanii yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  23,42,Refti Men fu…ó…ói …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe gire wo…ì…ìe goo
  23,43,"Mofte woo lajal majje ngal adotaako …óe, …ìe nennantaake kadi"
  23,44,"Refti Men Nuli Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen ko …ìe jokkondir…ìe, tuma kala ari e mofte Nulaa…óo majje on …ìe fenna mo Men jokkini yoga e ma…ì…ìe yoga, Men wa…ói …ìe yewtereeji, wo…ó…óineede wonanii yim…ìe …ìe gom…óintaa …ìen"
  23,45,Refti Men Nuli Muusaa e musi…ó…óo makko on Haaruuna wonndude e Aayeeje Amen …óen e hujja …ìanngu…óo
  23,46,"Faade e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'un ngun, …ìe mawnintinii …ìe laatii yim…ìe townitii…ìe"
  23,47,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enee, hara men gom…óinayyim…ìe …ói…óo yeru amen, hara yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe ko maccu…ìe amen"
  23,48,"∆Åe fenni …ìen …ói…óo, …ìe laatii jeyaa…ìe e halkaa…ìe …ìen"
  23,49,Gom…óii Men Okkiino Muusaa Deftere nden belejo'o kam…ìe …ìe feewa
  23,50,"Men wa…ói ge…óal Mariyama on e neene makko Maande, Men werni …ìe faade e tulde joomiraare √±i…ìrude e callungol"
  23,51,"Ko onon yo Nulaa…ìe, √±aamee immorde e laa…ìu…ói …óin gollon ko mo∆¥∆¥i, pellet Min, Mi…óo Anndi ko golloton kon"
  23,52,"E pellet, kaa Diina mo'on ko Diina woota, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on hulee Lam"
  23,53,"∆Åe ta∆¥i fiyaake ma…ì…ìe on hakkunde ma…ì…ìe dente, kala fedde no farnora ko woni kon ka mayre"
  23,54,∆äalu …ìe e siwrere nden haa e dummunne
  23,55,"Enee, hara …ìe sikku wonndema ko Men …ìeydiri …ìe kon immorde e jawdi e …ìi…ó…ìe"
  23,56,"Men yaccinanay …ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ereeji, ko woni …ìe so'aa"
  23,57,"Pellet, …ìen …ìe ka√±um immorde e kulol Joomi ma…ì…ìe hara ko …ìe hulu…ìe"
  23,58,E …ìen …ìe ka√±um ko …ìe gom…óin…ìe Aayeeje Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen
  23,59,E …ìen …ìe ka√±um …ìe wonah sirkanoo…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe
  23,60,"E …ìen okkay…ìe ko …ìe okkaa kon, hara …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ko hulu…óe [Alla], wonndema kam…ìe ko faade ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe …ìe ruttoytoo"
  23,61,"∆Åen [sifaa…ìe …óii sifaaji …óoo] hi…ìe yaccoo e mo∆¥∆¥ereeji …óin, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe adotoo…ìe e majji"
  23,62,"Men fawaali wonkii si wanaa fodde baw…óe makki, no ka Amen Deftere wowlaynde Goonga kan, hara kam…ìe …ìe too√±oytaake"
  23,63,"Ko woni, …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen no e welsungo immorde e …óum, no woodani …ìe kadi golle gaanin …óum ko kam…ìe gollate …óe"
  23,64,Haa si Men nanngirii neeminaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen Lepte …óen jaka yoo kam…ìe hi…ìe haaca
  23,65,"Wata on haacu hannde, pellet onon, on wallataake immorde e Amen"
  23,66,"Gom…óii laatinoke Aayeeje Amen …óen no janngee e taweede moo…óon, laati…óon hi…óon ruttoo e dow codduli moo…óon"
  23,67,"Ko on mawnintinii…ìe sabu [jeyeede makka] hi…óon hiira wowla bon…ói"
  23,68,"Enee, hara …ìe teskaaki konngol ngol, kaa hara aru e ma…ì…ìe ko araali e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe adinoo…ìe …ìen"
  23,69,"Kaa …ìe anndaali Nulaa…óo ma…ì…ìe on, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe faytu…ìe mo"
  23,70,"Kaa hara …ìe wi'ay feetere no e makko? Ko woni, o addanii …ìe Goonga kan …ìur…ìe heewude e ma…ì…ìe ko a√±u…ìe Goonga kan"
  23,71,"Sinndo Alqur'aana jokkuno belee…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin bonayno e …ìen wonu…ìe e majji, ko woni, Men addanii…ìe waaju ma…ì…ìe ngun, kam…ìe ko…ìe …óurnii…ìe gaayi waaju ma…ì…ìe ngun"
  23,72,"Kaa a tori …ìe ngeenaari? [Awa] ko ngeenaari Joomi maa…óa ndin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, ko Kanko woni Mo∆¥∆¥o Arsikoowo"
  23,73,"Pellet, an hi…óa noddude faade e Laawol Focciingol"
  23,74,"E pellet, …ìen …ìe gom…óinaali Laakara on ko …ìe selu…ìe e Laawol ngol"
  23,75,"Sinndo Men Yurmino …ìe, Men hunci ko he…ìi …ìe kon immorde e lorra, …ìe duumotono e nder bewre ma…ì…ìe hi…ìe wemmboo"
  23,76,"Gom…óii Men nanngirii …ìe Lepte …óen, …ìe hoykinanaaki Joomi ma…ì…ìe …ìe yankinaaki"
  23,77,"Haa si Men udditii e dow ma…ì…ìe dammbugal marungal Lepte sa…ótu…óe, e jaka, kam…ìe e nder …óum ko …ìe ta∆¥ii …ìe"
  23,78,"Ko Kanko woni On fu…ó…óan∆äo on nan…óe …óen e gii…óe …óen e …ìer…óe …óen, fan…óii ko yettoton"
  23,79,Ko Kanko woni On Tagu∆äo on ka leydi ko faade ka Makko moo…ìoyte…óon
  23,80,"Ko Kanko woni On Mo no wurna O wara no woodani Mo luutindirgol jemma on e √±alorma on, enee, kaa on hakkiltah"
  23,81,"Ko woni, …ìe wi'u yeru ko aram…ìe …ìen wi'unoo kon"
  23,82,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enee, si men maayii men wonii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e, hara menen ko men immintinoytee…ìe"
  23,83,"Gom…óii men fodanooma …óum menen e baabiraa…ìe amen ko adii, …óum wonaali si wanaa tinndi adinoo…ìe"
  23,84,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo leydi ndin woodani e …ìen wonu…ìe e mayri, si tawii hi…óon anndi"
  23,85,"Aray …ìe wi'a: \"Ko Alla woodani\" maaku: \"Enee, on waajitotaako"
  23,86,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo woni Jom kammuuli …óin jee…ói…ói e Jom Arsi mawki kin?\" @Corrected"
  23,87,"Aray …ìe wi'a: \"Ko Alla\" maaku: \"Enee, on hulatah [Alla]"
  23,88,"Maaku hommbo woni e Junngo Mu'un Laamu kala huunde hara Kanko hiMo walla O walletaake, si tawii on laatike hi…óon anndi"
  23,89,"Aray …ìe wi'a: \"Ko Alla woodani\" maaku: \"Enee, ko honno mbilirte…óon"
  23,90,"Ko woni, Men addanii …ìe Goonga kan, pellet kam…ìe ko …ìe fenu…ìe"
  23,91,"Alla jogitaaki …ìi…ó…óo, rewetee…óo laataaki wonndude e Makko, e jaka [si wa…óum wa…óuno] kala rewetee…óo yaadayno e ko o tagi kon, yoga e ma…ì…ìe townitotono e dow yoga. Senayee wonanii Alla e gaayi kon ko …ìe sifotoo"
  23,92,Anndu…óo ko wirnii kon e ko seedaa kon O Toowii e gaayi ko …ìe sirkata kon
  23,93,"Maaku: \"Jooma am si A hollii lam ko …ìe fodaa kon"
  23,94,"Jooma am, wata A wa…óam e yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  23,95,"Pellet, Menen fii yo Men holle ko Men fodi …ìe kon ko Men Hattan…ìe […óum]"
  23,96,"Du√±ir nden huunde …ìurnde mo∆¥∆¥ude [huunde] bonunde nden, ko Menen Anndi ko …ìe sifoto kon"
  23,97,"Maaku: \"Jooma, mi moolorii Ma immorde e kodooje Seytanuuji …óin"
  23,98,Mi moolorii Ma Jooma am nde …ói tawata lam
  23,99,"Haa si maayde arii e go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe nden, o wi'a: \"Jooma am ruttee lam"
  23,100,"Belajo'o men, mi gollay ko mo∆¥∆¥i e nder kon ko mi accunoo, …óum wa…óataa, ngol ko kanngol ko kanko wowli ngol, no hedde …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe heedo haa √ëalnde nde …ìe imminoytee"
  23,101,"Si wuttaama ka alaadu, haray askaaji alah hakkunde ma…ì…ìe nden √ëalnde, …ìe lanndandirtah"
  23,102,"Kala on mo jisti(teddi) manndake (peesirgal)muu…óum, haray ko …ìen …óon woni maloytee…ìe …ìen"
  23,103,"Kala mo manndake [mo∆¥∆¥i] muu…óum foygitii, (hoyi)haray ko …ìen …óon woni hayru…ìe pittaali muu…óum, ko ka nder Jahannama woni ko …ìe luttintee"
  23,104,"Yiite ngen no sunna geece ma…ì…ìe …óen, hara kam…ìe e nder magge ko …ìe √±ir…ìinii…ìe"
  23,105,"Enee, hara Aayeeje Am …óen laataaki no janngee e taweede mo'on, laati…óon hi…óon fenna …óe"
  23,106,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, ko malkiso amen ngon foolii men, men laatinoke yim…ìe majju…ìe"
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin men e magge, si men ruttike hara pellet, menen ko men too√±u…ìe"
  23,108,"O Daala: \"√ëii…ìee e nder magge wata on haalanam"
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen hi…ìe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, men gom…óinii haforan men Yurme∆äaa men ko An …ìuri Mo∆¥∆¥ude Yurmetee…ìe …ìen"
  23,110,"Jogiti…óon …ìe jalnori(jalkigol), haa …ìe yejjintini on ja≈ãta Am, laati…óon hi…óon jala …ìe"
  23,111,"Min Mi yo…ìii …ìe hannde sabu ko …ìe mu√±√±inoo kon, pellet, kam…ìe ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  23,112,"O Daali: \"No foti heewde ko √±ii…ìu…óon ka leydi, limoore duu…ìi"
  23,113,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men √±ii…ìii √±allal maa…óum yoga e √±allal, lanndo limoo…ìe …ìen"
  23,114,"O Daali: \"On √±ii…ìaali si wonaa see…óa, sinndo onon on laatino hi…óon anndi"
  23,115,"Enee, on sikku wonndema ko Men Tagiri on ko puyndan, hara onon on ruttetaake faade ka Amen"
  23,116,"Alla Toowii Laam…óo Goongu…óo On, Rewetee- …óo alah si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  23,117,"Kala noddu…óo wonndude e Alla rewetee…óo goo, daliil alanah mo e …óum, anndu pellet, hasboo- re makko ko ka Joomi makko, pellet Kanko, O malnatah heefer…ìe …ìen"
  23,118,"Maaku: \"Jooma am, Yaafo Yurmo ko An ∆Åuri Mo∆¥∆¥ude Yurmetee…ìe …ìen"